'''天主教馬林加總教區'''（{{lang-la|Archidioecesis Maringaënsis}}；{{lang-pt|Arquidiocese de Maringá}}）是[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]]在[[巴西|巴西]]的一個教省[[總教區|總教區]]，下轄3個教區。

教區於1956年2月1日成立<ref>{{cite book |title=ACTA APOSTOLICAE SEDIS |series=II |volume=XXIII |year=1956 |publisher=Typis Polyglottis Vaticanis |pages=485-488 |url=https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-48-1956-ocr.pdf |accessdate=2020-04-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200421185405/https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-48-1956-ocr.pdf |archivedate=2020-04-21 |language=la |dead-url=no }}</ref>，1979年10月16日升為總教區<ref>{{cite web |title=MARINGAËNSIS* |url=https://w2.vatican.va/content/john-paul-ii/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_jp-ii_apc_19791016_maringaensis.html |publisher=Libreria Editrice Vaticana |accessdate=2019-11-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191120131955/https://w2.vatican.va/content/john-paul-ii/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_jp-ii_apc_19791016_maringaensis.html |archivedate=2019-11-20 |language=la |date=1979-10-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

總教區位於[[巴拉那州|巴拉那州]]西北部，2004年時有428,157名教友，佔轄區總人口70.0%。教區下轄51個堂區，有59名司鐸。

現任總主教為{{link-pt|塞味利·克拉森|Severino Clasen}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Rinunce e nomine, 01.07.2020 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2020/07/01/0367/00850.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2020-07-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200701104237/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2020/07/01/0367/00850.html |archivedate=2020-07-01 |language=it |date=2020-07-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[宗座署理|宗座署理]]為{{link-pt|若望·馬梅德-菲爾奧|João Mamede Filho}}<ref name="Vatican20191120">{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 20.11.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/11/20/191120d.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-11-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191120130940/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/11/20/191120d.html |archivedate=2019-11-20 |language=en |date=2019-11-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休總主教為{{link-pt|阿努阿爾·巴蒂斯蒂|Anuar Battisti}}<ref name="Vatican20191120" />。

